Package: sdtt
Type: Package
Title: Simple Detection Theory Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
  person(
  given = "Stuart B.",
  family = "Moore",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  email = "s.b.moore@keele.ac.uk",
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0747-9304")
  )
Maintainer: Stuart B. Moore <s.b.moore@keele.ac.uk>
Description: A simple detection theory tool for calculating detection theory statistics.
  Assign conditional probabilities and calculate proportion of each conditional probability. 
  Raw totals for each conditional probability can also be requested by the user. Proportions
  can then be used to calculate various detection theory statistics such as d' and criterion.
Depends:
  dplyr
  R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
  dplyr
